 <fr:p>By induction on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>, with the base cases following from <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001A.xml" title="Dependent product of contractible types" addr="//erct/erct-001A" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001A" /></fr:link> and <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001B.xml" title="Dependent product of propositions" addr="//erct/erct-001B" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001B" /></fr:link> respectively. In the inductive step, we need to show that for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f,g\colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
